    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"depends on how it is practiced\" is a bit of a cop out lol. look at how people get cancelled for just having a different opinion online. doesnt that feel more like censorship than actual justice? like, isn't the whole point of social justice to be inclusive, but this feels like it's just excluding anyone who doesn't use the \"right\" language?",
